---
title: Easy BBQ Beef, Bacon & Veggie Filo Pie with Melted Cheddar Cheese
description: Look at this, it’s a pie that may be even better than the bakery’s best. Made in the comfort of your kitchen, the BBQ beef, bacon and
veggie filling is popping with sweetcorn, cheese and flavour. Serve it piping hot to complete this perfect pie picture.
